HOSPITAL LIEN
Notice is hereby given that Desert View Hospital has rendered services in hospitalization for NYLENE
STEGER , a person who was injured on 5/6/2022, in the city of LAS VEGAS, county of CLARK, and
that Desert View Hospital hereby claims a lien upon any money due or owing or any claim for
compensation, damages, contribution, settlement or judgment from State Farm, Claim no(s) 2833Q006X,
alleged to have caused the injuries, or any other person, corporation or association liable for the injury.
The hospitalization was rendered to the injured person between 5/6/2022 and 5/6/2022.
Attached please find "Exhibit A" as an Itemized Statement of Charges.
That 90 days have not elapsed since the termination of hospitalization; that the claimant's demands for
such care or service is in the sum of $ 7,915.76, and that no part thereof has been paid except $ 0.00
and that there is now due and owing and remaining unpaid of such sum, after deducting all credits and
offsets, the sum of $ 7,915.76, in which amount lien is hereby claimed.
Desert View Hospital, Claimant.
of Kamibra WN
Kamesha Williams
TPL Specialist, Elevate PFS
Agent for Desert View Hospital
ACKNOWLEDGMENT
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF MONTGOMERY
I, Kamesha Williams, being first duly sworn, on oath say:
That I am Kamesha Williams, named in the foregoing claim of lien; that I have read the same and know
the contents thereof and believe the same to be true.
Signed and subscribed before me on 06/29/2022
